    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>To install Openjdk 11 in Ubuntu, the following commands worked well.</p>\n\n<pre><code>sudo add-apt-repository ppa:openjdk-r/ppa\nsudo apt-get update\nsudo apt install openjdk-11-jdk\n</code></pre>\n"
